high_descs: move straight to the sink
pick up the knife
move right to the sink
slice the tomato in the sink
drop the knife in the sink
pick up the tomato slice
turn around to the oven
drop the tomato to cook in the oven and take it out
turn left and head to the shelf
drop the tomato slice on the shelf
anns.task_desc: drop a cooked tomato slice on the shelf

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, turn left and go to the edge of the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter above the egg.
Turn right, step forward, turn left to face the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink below the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around and walk towards the hall, turn left and walk to microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato inside, close the door. Turn on microwave for a few seconds, open door, remove tomato, and close the door.
Return to the kitchen counter where there will be a table to the left.
Lean the tomato slice upwards on the dispenser next to the cup.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of tomato and place on table.

high_descs: Walk straight, past the refrigerator, then turn right at the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife between the salt and pepper, on the counter.
Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Place the knife in the sink in front of the tomato.
Pick up one of the tomato slices.
Turn around and walk to the white table, then turn to your left and go to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato slice from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, then turn right at the white table and go to the black table in the corner.
Place the tomato slice on the black table, between the coffee cup and the other tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato slice on the table.
